data.description: Reduced and assumable!! This updated 3 bedroom, 2 bath home is quite spacious! Has two living areas or the additional room can be a family room, office, bedroom or game room. Upgraded kitchen with two dining areas. Cozy up to the wood burning fireplace while enjoying the large living space looking out to the private patio area. Nice kitchen with upgraded gas stove and nice counter tops. This has a private spacious primary suite with its own bath and access to the back yard patio area. This could be great as the primary or an in-law suite. There's room to roam for a large family with the split bedroom floorplan. New flooring in main areas. Nicely finished bathrooms. Two car garage with storage or workshop area. Create your oasis on the huge lot tucked way in the back with beautiful shade trees for all your outdoor family fun. This convenient location is close to all of Greenville amenities. Good schools, shopping and restaurants. Has a VA 2.49% loan that can be assumed by a non veteran.
